tasks.description:
In each service that uses Redis or Kafka, replace hardcoded connection values with environment variable placeholders:
- spring.data.redis.host: ${REDIS_HOST:localhost}
- spring.data.redis.password: ${REDIS_AUTH_TOKEN:}
- spring.kafka.bootstrap-servers: ${KAFKA_BOOTSTRAP_SERVERS:localhost:9092}
- spring.kafka.properties.sasl.jaas.config: references ${MSK_SASL_USERNAME} and ${MSK_SASL_PASSWORD}
- application.jwt.secret: ${JWT_SECRET:dev-only-insecure-default}
Apply JWT_SECRET placeholder to api-gateway and identity-service only.
